text: Émilie Volle (born 8 October 1981) is a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint-Étienne
